* `exam-summary.md` → Full exam overview
* `one_pager.md` → Last-minute review
* `exam_traps.md` → Common pitfalls
* `glossary.md` → Key terms

---

## 💡 Final Thought

This repository is designed not only to pass the AZ-900 exam, but also to build a solid foundation for further Azure certifications like AZ-204.

